<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="summary-n">summary <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'sʌməri/    美 /'sʌməri/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>总结；摘要；概要：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>in summary</strong> 
总的来说</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Can you give me a quick <strong>summary of</strong> your research?
你能给我简要概括一下你的研究工作吗？</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>summarise / summarize /'sʌməraɪz/ v vi &amp; vt  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>To summarise, this is a clever approach to a common problem. 
总而言之，这是一个解决常见问题的巧妙方法。</p></div></div>